twoSetSkill.name: Redemptive Resurrection 2 Pieces
twoSetSkill.description: Lightning DMG increases by 30.0%. Casting Ultimate triggers the effects of all equipped stigma pieces (triggering it again refreshes the duration).

threeSetSkill.name: Praise of Heaven 3 Pieces
threeSetSkill.description: Teammates on the field gain 20.0% Total DMG Multiplier (cannot stack). Upon spending at least 60/120 SP in one go, all enemies take 10.0%/35.0% bonus Lightning DMG for 20s (can be refreshed but cannot stack).
